Hector_quadrotor_demo (TungNV)

Tutorial:
http://wiki.ros.org/hector_quadrotor/Tutorials

Fix bug while building:
https://answers.ros.org/question/244776/is-it-possible-to-run-the-hector_quadrotor-demos-in-kinetic/

Run simulation:
1. Run Gazebo and Rviz:
roslaunch hector_quadrotor_demo indoor_slam_gazebo.launch
or
roslaunch hector_quadrotor_demo outdoor_flight_gazebo.launch

2. Open new terminal, enable motor:
rosservice call /enable_motors "enable: true"

3. Controller the quadrotor via keyboard:
rosrun teleop_twist_keyboard teleop_twist_keyboard.py

